Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉 路上堵车了\N{\r英文}Sorry, there was traffic jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,最讨厌早班了\N{\r英文}I hate the morning shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们吐得到处都是\N{\r英文}There was always vomit everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就像前几天在七子通公园厕所一样…\N{\r英文}Like the other day at Nanago Dori Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就在涩谷的幡谷\N{\r英文}...in Hatagaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太可怕了\N{\r英文}It was truly terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个昏迷很久的人\N{\r英文}There is someone who has been out for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太恐怖了 十分可以打八分\N{\r英文}The horror level is 8 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在听我说话吗\N{\r英文}Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不用麻烦了 桧山先生 反正没过多久还是会变脏\N{\r英文}No need to bother, Mr. Hiyarama. It'll get dirty again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\r英文}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\r英文}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是妈妈带你过来的吗\N{\r英文}Are you here with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事儿的\N{\r英文}Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,仗助\N{\r英文}Josuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈正在找你呢\N{\r英文}Mom is looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人啊\N{\r英文}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈在到处找你呢\N{\r英文}Mom is looking for you everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是跟你说不要走得太远吗\N{\r英文}Didn't Mom say not to go too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在公园里到处找你呢\N{\r英文}Mom is looking all over the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈\N{\r英文}I'm sorry Mom, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在弟弟也哭了\N{\r英文}Now he was crying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈\N{\r英文}I'm sorry mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在好了\N{\r英文}Now it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这要怎么用\N{\r英文}How does this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 欢迎光临\N{\r英文}Hello, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.54,0:25:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\r英文}Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.58,0:25:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,犒劳一下你\N{\r英文}For your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.25,0:25:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 他打中了\N{\r英文}Yes! He hit the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.50,0:25:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 没错吧\N{\r英文}He's in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.25,0:25:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了没\N{\r英文}He's in! Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.37,0:25:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你干嘛\N{\r英文}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.37,0:25:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,打赌吗 这有什么好玩儿的\N{\r英文}Playing bets? Where's the fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.75,0:25:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,凯酱 退后\N{\r英文}Kat-chan! Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.95,0:25:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要尊重别人支持的队伍或者是宗教什么的 来击个掌\N{\r英文}Always respect other people's sports teams or religions. High five!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.91,0:26:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回去吧\N{\r英文}Now go away. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.79,0:26:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们作弊了\N{\r英文}They cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.20,0:26:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把其他队里厉害的球手挖走了\N{\r英文}They steal great players from other teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.37,0:33:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\r英文}Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.66,0:33:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,绫 你来啦\N{\r英文}Aya! You come!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.62,0:33:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,百分之百的惊喜\N{\r英文}What a surprise! The rating is 10 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.12,0:33:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等 还剩最后一个地方了\N{\r英文}Wait a moment! This is the last place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.16,0:33:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就结束了\N{\r英文}I'm about to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.25,0:33:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你还是能很有效率地工作呀\N{\r英文}Turns out you can work fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有个女孩在等我呢 我要下班了\N{\r英文}There's a girl waiting for me. I'm done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.16,0:34:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\r英文}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.16,0:34:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 你的车能借我用一下吗\N{\r英文}Mr Hiyarama, may I borrow your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.83,0:34:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 我可不能错过今天晚上的机会\N{\r英文}I can't miss this opportunity tonight. Mr. Hiyarama, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.87,0:34:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\r英文}I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\r英文}Come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.37,0:34:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的前辈 桧山先生\N{\r英文}This is Mr. Hiyarama, my senior at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.79,0:34:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,认真勤勉 而且还很安静\N{\r英文}Hard worker, but very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.87,0:34:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可没有人这么说过我\N{\r英文}I don't even know what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.20,0:34:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 这是绫\N{\r英文}Mr. Hiyarama, this is Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.83,0:34:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对的满分女孩\N{\r英文}Definitely a 10 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.87,0:34:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说了\N{\r英文}Stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.62,0:34:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个还能放吗\N{\r英文}Can this be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.37,0:35:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\r英文}Pak Hiyarama..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.79,0:35:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个声音\N{\r英文}I like the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.50,0:35:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\r英文}Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.54,0:35:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,史密斯\N{\r英文}Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.29,0:35:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很常见的名字\N{\r英文}Very common name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.37,0:35:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\r英文}Pak Hiyarama,...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.29,0:36:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,…你真的喜欢这份工作吗\N{\r英文}...do you really like this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.70,0:36:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至有自己的设备和工具\N{\r英文}You have your own equipment and tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.12,0:36:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这种工作你为什么还要这么努力呢\N{\r英文}How can you work so hard at a job like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.41,0:36:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不必回答我\N{\r英文}You don't have to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.45,0:36:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇\N{\r英文}I'm just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.54,0:36:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人很奇怪\N{\r英文}This person is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.41,0:36:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,满分十分可以打九分\N{\r英文}The scale is oddly 9 out of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.25,0:36:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢盒式磁带的声音\N{\r英文}I like the sound of cassette recordings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.33,0:36:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 卡带的声音听起来很棒\N{\r英文}Yes! The cassette sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.58,0:36:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次听\N{\r英文}This is my first time listening to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.08,0:36:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次总是最好的\N{\r英文}The first time is always good!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.12,0:36:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿把我放下\N{\r英文}Drop me off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.83,0:36:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是在约会吗\N{\r英文}Aren't we on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.54,0:36:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,酒吧要加班\N{\r英文}I have an extra shift at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.04,0:36:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你来的话 我可以陪你一晚上\N{\r英文}If you come, I'll be with you all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.04,0:36:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没发工资呢\N{\r英文}I'm still waiting for my salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.95,0:37:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 这对我来说非常重要\N{\r英文}Mr. Hiyarama, this is very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.45,0:37:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人没钱的话还谈什么恋爱啊\N{\r英文}People can't fall in love without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.37,0:37:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界到底怎么了\N{\r英文}What happened to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.95,0:37:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是现代吗\N{\r英文}Is this the modern era?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.37,0:37:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个值多少钱啊\N{\r英文}What is the price for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.20,0:37:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想知道吗\N{\r英文}Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.83,0:38:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇\N{\r英文}I'm just curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.12,0:38:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西又流行起来了 没准儿这些很值钱呢\N{\r英文}Analog is back in trend. All of this may be of great value.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.83,0:38:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的只是好奇而已 我知道下北有一个估价地地方\N{\r英文}I'm really just curious! I know a suitable place in Shimokita.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去\N{\r英文}I didn't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.50,0:38:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,都用不上三十分钟\N{\r英文}It only takes less than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.20,0:38:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就在这里的...\N{\r英文}It should be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.50,0:38:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里 看到了吧\N{\r英文}Here, that's the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.41,0:38:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,借过\N{\r英文}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.58,0:38:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 这个现在值多少\N{\r英文}Excuse me, how much is the selling price for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.29,0:38:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,卢·里德的磁带很少见啊\N{\r英文}This one is rare, it's Lou Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.83,0:38:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个的话值12000日元\N{\r英文}For this, 12 thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\r英文}Very?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.95,0:38:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个值8000  - 真的吗\N{\r英文}- For this 8000.   - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.87,0:38:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这些磁带你是从哪儿弄到的\N{\r英文}Where did you get these tapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.00,0:39:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的前辈的\N{\r英文}They belong to my seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.04,0:39:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这个得有4000日元\N{\r英文}This one is 4000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.12,0:39:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这盘差不多6000 你手里的这些值很多钱呢\N{\r英文}This one can be sold for 6000. You can make a lot of money from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.79,0:39:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这还只是估计\N{\r英文}This is my estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.00,0:39:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\r英文}My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.62,0:39:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 我们把这些都卖掉吧\N{\r英文}Extraordinary! Mr. Hiyarama, let's sell all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.45,0:39:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的我们都要 现在这个很流行\N{\r英文}We accept everything. Cassettes are trending.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.29,0:39:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是七八十年代的磁带\N{\r英文}Especially cassettes from the 70s and 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.70,0:39:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把你的收藏都卖了吧\N{\r英文}We have to sell it, your entire collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.91,0:39:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,光是这盘就值12000\N{\r英文}Twelve thousand just for this tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.95,0:39:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正是时候\N{\r英文}Now is the perfect time!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.41,0:39:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一个 就卖一个也行\N{\r英文}OK, just one. We'll just sell one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.83,0:39:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就可以去酒吧见绫了 今晚对我真的很重要\N{\r英文}Then I can go to the bar to meet Aya. This is a very important night for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.20,0:39:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很重要\N{\r英文}This is a very important night for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.08,0:39:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我错过这个机会...\N{\r英文}If I miss this opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.37,0:40:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没有钱还哪有什么爱情生活 是吧\N{\r英文}No love life if we're broke? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.91,0:40:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\r英文}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.58,0:40:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,恩人 我先走了\N{\r英文}You saved me! I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.66,0:40:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你最棒了 桧山先生\N{\r英文}You're the best, Mr. Hiyarama!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.45,0:41:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎下次光临\N{\r英文}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.79,0:54:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\r英文}Thank You!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.04,0:54:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\r英文}Pak Hiyarama..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.41,0:54:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我跟绫不会在一起了 大概只有两成的机会\N{\r英文}I don't think it's possible for me to be with Aya. Chances are 2 out of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.08,0:54:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不会放弃的放弃\N{\r英文}But that doesn't mean I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.79,0:54:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生...\N{\r英文}Pak Hiyarama..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.75,0:54:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没结婚吧\N{\r英文}You're not married yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.58,0:54:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个年纪还一个人\N{\r英文}Alone at your age..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.04,0:54:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会觉得孤独吗\N{\r英文}Don't you ever feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.95,0:54:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,高志\N{\r英文}Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.41,0:54:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\r英文}It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.83,0:54:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,高志\N{\r英文}Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.54,0:54:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们已经很久没见面了  - 高志\N{\r英文}- We haven't seen each other for a long time.  - Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.08,0:55:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗\N{\r英文}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.25,0:55:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找你呢\N{\r英文}I am looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.08,0:55:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗  - 是啊\N{\r英文}- Very?   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.58,0:55:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 这是我的好朋友寺酱\N{\r英文}Mr. Hiyarama, this is Dera-chan, my good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.62,0:55:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧 他很喜欢我的耳朵\N{\r英文}As you can see, he likes my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.91,0:55:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,每次见面都会握住\N{\r英文}Every time he meets me, he holds it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.83,0:55:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不管我到哪里 他总是能找到我\N{\r英文}He always finds me. 10 out of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.04,0:55:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢我的耳朵 ...\N{\r英文}Dera-chan likes my ears,...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.41,0:55:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我都要变成什么挂件了\N{\r英文}...and I'm just the accessory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.45,0:55:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 是吧\N{\r英文}- Yes. -  Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.54,0:56:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这个还给你\N{\r英文}I want to return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.33,0:56:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\r英文}Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.00,0:56:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我能再听一遍吗\N{\r英文}Can I listen to it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.00,0:57:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.58,0:57:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,贵司有跟你说什么吗\N{\r英文}Did Takashi tell you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.66,0:59:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\r英文}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.33,0:59:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是犒劳你的\N{\r英文}For your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.58,1:03:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.58,1:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,文库新书 每本100日元\N{\r英文}100 YEN FOR THE BOOKS
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.83,1:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,幸田文【日本女作家】应该更出名的\N{\r英文}Aya Koda should be more famous.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.12,1:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然她的遣词很日常 但是依旧很特别\N{\r英文}He uses common word choices, but is still special.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.41,1:07:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好 桧山先生\N{\r英文}Good evening, Mr. Hiyarama.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.54,1:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还是老样子吗\N{\r英文}The usual message?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.04,1:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在读什么\N{\r英文}What are you reading now?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.83,1:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,幸田文的木\N{\r英文}Aya Koda "Pohon".
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.62,1:07:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,散文吗\N{\r英文}The essay?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.54,1:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你读过吗\N{\r英文}Have you read it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.79,1:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有学识\N{\r英文}You're very educated.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.91,1:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不这么觉得\N{\r英文}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.62,1:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的土豆沙拉...\N{\r英文}Here's your potato salad...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.00,1:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还有酒水...\N{\r英文}...and here's to a long day.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.08,1:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘 我们怎么都没有前菜\N{\r英文}Mom, we didn't get the appetizer.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.75,1:07:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 肯定有的\N{\r英文}I'm sure I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.37,1:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那也没有这么多\N{\r英文}We never got that much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.08,1:07:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 我对大家可是一视同仁的\N{\r英文}That is not true. We're all equal here, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.58,1:07:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我可得去字典里查查这个词\N{\r英文}I had to look up the word "equality" in the dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.95,1:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,女人可不喜欢多嘴的男人\N{\r英文}Women don't like talkative men.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.08,1:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你这里一直有皱纹吗\N{\r英文}Have you always had wrinkles here?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.20,1:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 就一个 在那里\N{\r英文}No, the only one. There.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.83,1:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘 还有炸豆腐吗\N{\r英文}Mama, do you have fried tofu?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.12,1:08:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已经卖光了  你要的话我一会儿去做\N{\r英文}No, it's finished. I'll make it later if you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.79,1:08:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他的妻子丢下他走了\N{\r英文}His wife left him, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.20,1:08:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么还这么开心呢\N{\r英文}How could he be so cheerful?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.95,1:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是在说我吗\N{\r英文}Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.20,1:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\r英文}There isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.45,1:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我的妻子离开我了 我还这么高兴\N{\r英文}How can you be cheerful when your wife left you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.33,1:08:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单啊 因为我终于可以没有负担地一个人生活了\N{\r英文}That is easy. Finally I can live alone again without burdens.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.20,1:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,任谁都会很开心的\N{\r英文}It makes all men happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.08,1:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,能够摆脱挑挑拣拣的女人真是一种解脱\N{\r英文}It's a relief to be able to get rid of fussy women.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.62,1:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还强撑着呢\N{\r英文}You pretend to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.20,1:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,过不了多久 你就要跟老板娘哭诉你有多孤独了\N{\r英文}Soon you will confide in Mama how lonely you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.66,1:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,左不过是些无聊的故事\N{\r英文}Just boring stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.29,1:08:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要再来一杯吗\N{\r英文}Want another drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.62,1:08:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,请\N{\r英文}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.37,1:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么世界上没有能保持不变的事物呢\N{\r英文}Why can't everything stay the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.41,1:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘\N{\r英文}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.87,1:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们唱那首歌吧\N{\r英文}Sing us that song.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.66,1:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的最爱\N{\r英文}Our favorite.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.45,1:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那首啊\N{\r英文}Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.29,1:09:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但桧山先生才刚到\N{\r英文}But Mr. Hiyarama had just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.79,1:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我们难过呀\N{\r英文}Don't disappoint us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.95,1:09:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就是呀\N{\r英文}Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.79,1:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\r英文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.08,1:09:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你已经拿出吉他了...\N{\r英文}Since you've already got the guitar out... Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.54,1:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一首优美的歌曲\N{\r英文}This is a beautiful song.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.45,1:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我到了一个叫\N{\r英文}I got to the place
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.83,1:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,新奥尔良的地方\N{\r英文}in New Orleans
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.45,1:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,到了一家叫旭日之屋\N{\r英文}to a place called a brothel
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.87,1:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,的妓院\N{\r英文}"House of the Rising Sun"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.20,1:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱的男人\N{\r英文}The man I love
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.75,1:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有回来\N{\r英文}he didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.12,1:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那时我离开了\N{\r英文}That's when I left
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.66,1:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的祖国\N{\r英文}your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.16,1:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我上了火车\N{\r英文}I got on the train,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.41,1:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有回头...\N{\r英文}and in a matter of seconds...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.12,1:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两杯柠檬水\N{\r英文}And two lemonades!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.62,1:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你来啦 稍等一下\N{\r英文}You've arrived, just wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.04,1:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\r英文}For your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.37,1:14:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\r英文}Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.12,1:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪来的\N{\r英文}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.45,1:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经等你很久了\N{\r英文}I've been waiting for you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.33,1:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你家是哪扇门\N{\r英文}Which door is your house?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.25,1:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,楼上还是楼下\N{\r英文}Upstairs or downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.95,1:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是Niko吗\N{\r英文}Niko?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.70,1:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你长这么大了\N{\r英文}You're big!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.87,1:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔...\N{\r英文}Uncle,...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.54,1:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,…你要上班吗\N{\r英文}...you're going to work?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.41,1:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以一起去吗\N{\r英文}can i come along
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.79,1:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该让我跟着的\N{\r英文}Uncle should let me come along.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.75,1:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人的话可不知道会做出什么事情\N{\r英文}I don't know what I would do if I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.08,1:17:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,从那边上\N{\r英文}Enter from the next door.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.00,1:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要咖啡吗\N{\r英文}Would you like coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.58,1:17:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要\N{\r英文}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.66,1:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一样吗\N{\r英文}The same as me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.00,1:17:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.79,1:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.87,1:18:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要放进去吗  - 是的\N{\r英文}- Do you want to set it? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.70,1:18:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\r英文}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.16,1:18:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是这边\N{\r英文}This side.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.50,1:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 像这样吗  - 是的\N{\r英文}- Like this?  -  Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.50,1:18:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,磁带卷在这边\N{\r英文}The tape is on this side.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.87,1:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是东京晴空塔吗\N{\r英文}What is Sky Tree tower?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.95,1:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Oh, benar.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.91,1:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 这就是盒式录音带\N{\r英文}So, this is a cassette?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.00,1:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是你那个年代的吗\N{\r英文}From ancient times?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.95,1:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r英文}From ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.75,1:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我能在 iPhone上播放吗\N{\r英文}Can I play this on my iPhone?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.50,1:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这写的是什么\N{\r英文}What is it written?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.66,1:19:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,范·莫里森\N{\r英文}Van Morrison.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.12,1:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Spotify上有吗\N{\r英文}Is this on Spotify?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.29,1:19:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不懂\N{\r英文}Uncle doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.00,1:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\r英文}Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.83,1:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\r英文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.87,1:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的那家店\N{\r英文}That shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.04,1:19:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是一家商店\N{\r英文}It's not a shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.12,1:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 这个\N{\r英文}Ah, that!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.75,1:22:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说这个吗  我的相机已经很旧了\N{\r英文}You mean this? My camera is quite old.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.70,1:22:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\r英文}Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.54,1:22:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\r英文}How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.08,1:22:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗\N{\r英文}You do not remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.58,1:22:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是你送我的 叔叔\N{\r英文}You gave it to me, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.70,1:22:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊 是啊  - 说谎\N{\r英文}- Oh yes. - Lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.20,1:22:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了 对吧\N{\r英文}You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.91,1:22:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这棵树是你的朋友吗\N{\r英文}Is the tree your friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.91,1:22:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友吗\N{\r英文}Friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.75,1:22:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不是吗\N{\r英文}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.16,1:22:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你说得对\N{\r英文}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.29,1:22:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的树...朋友\N{\r英文}This is my friend.. Tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.75,1:24:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\r英文}Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.83,1:24:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以借这本书吗\N{\r英文}can i borrow this book
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.50,1:24:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本\N{\r英文}Which one?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.00,1:24:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,十一篇短篇小说\N{\r英文}"Eleven Short Stories."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.16,1:24:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\r英文}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.04,1:24:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,波兰龟那篇里的男孩 维克多…\N{\r英文}This boy, Victor, from the tale "The Polam Turtle"...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.91,1:24:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他就跟我一样\N{\r英文}He's like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.75,1:25:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我能理解他正在经历什么\N{\r英文}I understand what he is going through.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.12,1:25:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮你吗\N{\r英文}can i help
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.83,1:25:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.33,1:25:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔 你为什么跟妈妈合不来啊\N{\r英文}Uncle, why don't you and mother get along?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.12,1:26:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她这么说的吗\N{\r英文}He told you that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.20,1:26:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我谈到你...\N{\r英文}Every time I talk about you...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.20,1:26:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她都会转移话题\N{\r英文}...he changed the topic.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.12,1:26:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊\N{\r英文}So.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.75,1:26:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你和妈妈吵架了吗\N{\r英文}Did you quarrel with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.00,1:26:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\r英文}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.95,1:26:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是离家出走吗\N{\r英文}Do you always run away from home?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.37,1:26:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第一次\N{\r英文}This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.70,1:26:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直计划着跟叔叔一起生活\N{\r英文}It was always my plan to stay with Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.62,1:26:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 这算什么\N{\r英文}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.41,1:27:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我是去那边吗\N{\r英文}Thank You. Am I coming here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.37,1:27:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 十分钟后见  - 这也太短了\N{\r英文}- See you in 10 minutes. - That's too short.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.16,1:27:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那就二十分钟\N{\r英文}Then 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.87,1:27:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我明白\N{\r英文}Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.66,1:27:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 知道\N{\r英文}Yes, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.95,1:27:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗\N{\r英文}Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.04,1:27:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们去吃午饭吧  - 太好了\N{\r英文}- Then we'll have lunch.  -  Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.91,1:27:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 毛巾放这里  - 谢谢\N{\r英文}- Put the towel here. - Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.41,1:27:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你和妈妈一点都不像\N{\r英文}Uncle and mother are nothing alike.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.70,1:27:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你指的是哪方面\N{\r英文}You mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.25,1:28:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我们是不同世界的人\N{\r英文}He said Uncle and we live in different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.29,1:28:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该是真的吧\N{\r英文}That's probably true.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.25,1:28:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\r英文}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.62,1:28:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界就是这样形形色色\N{\r英文}This world consists of many different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.33,1:28:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,相关联的 不相关的\N{\r英文}Some are related and some are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.25,1:28:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的世界...\N{\r英文}My world...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.16,1:28:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你母亲的世界非常不同\N{\r英文}...and your mother's world is very different.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.25,1:28:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那我呢\N{\r英文}What about my world?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.20,1:28:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我身处哪个世界呢\N{\r英文}Where in the world am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.08,1:28:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这条河会流入大海吗\N{\r英文}This river flows into the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.66,1:28:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Yes, to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.25,1:28:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去那里吗\N{\r英文}Are you going there?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.45,1:29:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下次吧\N{\r英文}Next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.16,1:29:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\N{\r英文}When is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.37,1:29:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,下次就是下次\N{\r英文}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.58,1:29:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,具体呢\N{\r英文}When exactly?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.37,1:29:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,下次就是下次\N{\r英文}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.20,1:29:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就是现在\N{\r英文}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.62,1:29:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 下次\N{\r英文}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.29,1:29:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 现在\N{\r英文}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.29,1:29:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 下次\N{\r英文}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.70,1:29:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 现在\N{\r英文}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.12,1:29:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,下次 下次\N{\r英文}Next time, next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.33,1:29:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 现在\N{\r英文}Now yes now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.37,1:30:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐\N{\r英文}Sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.87,1:30:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见\N{\r英文}Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.91,1:30:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你就住在这里吗\N{\r英文}So you live here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.25,1:30:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有恶意 Niko 拿上你的东西\N{\r英文}I don't mean anything bad. Niko, get your things.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.70,1:30:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不要  - 我不是在跟你商量\N{\r英文}- Don't want to!  - That's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.95,1:30:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\r英文}Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.62,1:30:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快\N{\r英文}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.20,1:30:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\r英文}Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.41,1:30:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你愿意 你随时都可以来\N{\r英文}Come visit whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.58,1:30:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的书我还没读完呢\N{\r英文}I haven't even finished reading your book.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.25,1:30:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,带着吧\N{\r英文}Just bring it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.04,1:31:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我会像维克多一样\N{\r英文}I will be like Victor.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.08,1:31:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\r英文}Won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.75,1:31:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别这么说  - Niko\N{\r英文}- Do not say like that.   - Niko!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.33,1:31:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了\N{\r英文}Here's to your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.37,1:31:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是你最喜欢的巧克力\N{\r英文}Your favorite chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.04,1:31:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个好孩子\N{\r英文}He is a good child.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.54,1:31:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不敢说\N{\r英文}I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.79,1:31:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的父亲...\N{\r英文}Our father...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.91,1:32:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经什么都不认识了\N{\r英文}...he doesn't recognize anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.04,1:32:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去疗养院探望他吗\N{\r英文}Are you going to visit him at the nursing home?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.37,1:32:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他再也不会和以前一样了\N{\r英文}He will never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.29,1:32:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的在清扫厕所吗\N{\r英文}Is it true that you work cleaning toilets?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.20,1:32:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N{\r英文}Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.95,1:32:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank You.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.58,1:35:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是高志\N{\r英文}Hello, this is Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.33,1:35:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高志 你好\N{\r英文}This is Takashi, hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.41,1:35:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了\N{\r英文}I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.54,1:35:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,桧山先生 您对我很好 对此 我真的非常感激\N{\r英文}Mr. Hiyarama, you have been kind to me. I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.00,1:35:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,满分十分可以打九分\N{\r英文}The rating is 9 out of 10!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.37,1:35:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我很难当面跟你讲 我辞职了\N{\r英文}That's why it's hard for me to say this, but I resign.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.37,1:35:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\r英文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.66,1:35:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,钱我会马上还你的\N{\r英文}I will immediately reimburse you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.66,1:36:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 那谁来替你\N{\r英文}Wait, what about your sif?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.08,1:36:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\r英文}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.83,1:36:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们短期内找不到替代者\N{\r英文}We can't find a replacement anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.37,1:36:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那我应该怎么办\N{\r英文}No replacement? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.54,1:36:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那你今天就只能加班了\N{\r英文}You have to fill the shift today.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.04,1:36:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我会很快的\N{\r英文}what can Sorry, I'll be brief.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.62,1:36:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\r英文}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.08,1:36:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\r英文}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.66,1:36:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是新来的吗  - 我马上结束了\N{\r英文}- Are you new?   - I'm about to finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.58,1:37:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\r英文}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.08,1:37:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他人呢\N{\r英文}Where's Takashi?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.20,1:37:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经打过三遍电话了 为什么没人接\N{\r英文}I've called three times. Why isn't anyone picking up?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.62,1:38:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能顶一天\N{\r英文}I'm just doing it for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.08,1:38:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧找个新人\N{\r英文}Find someone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.04,1:39:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我是佐藤 是被派到这里的...\N{\r英文}I'm Sato. I was told to come here immediately...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.04,1:39:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...来顶替之前的人的班次\N{\r英文}...and took over the shift from the previous employee.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.58,1:40:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是从那里开始吗\N{\r英文}Should I start there?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.95,1:40:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.75,1:43:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\r英文}- Hello - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.62,1:44:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得这之前是什么吗\N{\r英文}Do you remember what this used to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.50,1:44:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经老了\N{\r英文}That means we are old.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.95,1:45:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里夏·海史密斯【美国女作家】对焦虑了如指掌\N{\r英文}Patricia Highsmith knows all about anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.79,1:45:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她告诉读者恐惧和焦虑完全是不同的东西\N{\r英文}He showed me that fear and anxiety are different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.45,1:45:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你这人是怎么回事\N{\r英文}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.54,1:45:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就是..\N{\r英文}You know..
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.41,1:45:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我能进来吗\N{\r英文}can i come in
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.95,1:46:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\r英文}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.87,1:46:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跟香烟一起打包好了\N{\r英文}Packed cigarettes and plastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.62,1:47:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以来一只吗\N{\r英文}Can I have one?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.58,1:48:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经很久没有抽烟了\N{\r英文}I haven't smoked for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.04,1:48:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的那个人是你吗\N{\r英文}Did you see us at the bar earlier?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.04,1:49:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你是个常客\N{\r英文}It seems like you always go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.79,1:49:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Of.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.70,1:49:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从开业至今已有五六年了\N{\r英文}It's been five or six years since the place opened.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.87,1:49:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样\N{\r英文}So it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.62,1:49:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一个很好的地方\N{\r英文}It's a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.91,1:49:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她的前夫\N{\r英文}I'm her ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.58,1:49:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\r英文}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.95,1:49:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离婚已经快七年了\N{\r英文}It's been about seven years since we divorced.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.83,1:49:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经再婚了\N{\r英文}I've remarried.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.08,1:49:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,距离上次见他已经七年了\N{\r英文}It's been seven years since I last saw him.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.41,1:49:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我得了癌症\N{\r英文}I have cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.33,1:50:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,癌细胞一直在扩散\N{\r英文}The cancer has spread.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.33,1:50:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身体因为化疗十分不堪\N{\r英文}My body was swollen from chemotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.00,1:50:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我...\N{\r英文}Then I...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.54,1:50:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,……突然觉得自己欠她一个道歉\N{\r英文}...suddenly felt that I owed him an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.62,1:50:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,以为我挺过去了\N{\r英文}Nothing bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.08,1:50:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是道歉\N{\r英文}Maybe not an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.45,1:50:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我要感谢她\N{\r英文}I want to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.79,1:50:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可能也不是\N{\r英文}No, it's not about that either.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.87,1:50:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想见见她 仅此而已\N{\r英文}I just want to see him, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.37,1:50:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来一瓶吗\N{\r英文}Do you want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.16,1:50:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩一瓶\N{\r英文}I still have one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.87,1:51:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗...\N{\r英文}In that case,...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.66,1:51:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\r英文}...I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.20,1:51:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请照顾好她\N{\r英文}Please take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.33,1:51:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我们不是那种关系  - 拜托你了\N{\r英文}- No, we don't have that kind of relationship.  - I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.16,1:51:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一个食客\N{\r英文}We don't have a relationship like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.91,1:51:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那些阴影..\N{\r英文}Shadow..
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.25,1:51:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被覆盖之后会变得更黑吗\N{\r英文}Do they get darker when overwritten?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.00,1:52:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道你\N{\r英文}Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.12,1:52:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有那么多不理解的事情呢\N{\r英文}There are so many things I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.45,1:52:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,生命就这样结束了\N{\r英文}That's how life ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.62,1:52:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真不甘心啊\N{\r英文}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.62,1:52:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在就去验证一下吧\N{\r英文}Let's find out now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.62,1:52:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\r英文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.50,1:52:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,站在那\N{\r英文}Stand there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.33,1:52:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\r英文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.54,1:52:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么\N{\r英文}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.62,1:53:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来一样啊\N{\r英文}Looks the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.70,1:53:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是更黑了吗\N{\r英文}Isn't it darker?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.58,1:53:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有吧\N{\r英文}Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.45,1:53:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说这看起来更黑了\N{\r英文}That looks darker to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.70,1:53:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是看不出有什么区别\N{\r英文}I don't see the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.41,1:53:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 看\N{\r英文}Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.54,1:53:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色要深一点才有意义\N{\r英文}The shade needs to be darker to make sense!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.87,1:53:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是太执着了\N{\r英文}You're so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.83,1:53:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没什么变化\N{\r英文}Still no changes?
